column1: Daily Weather Observations for Glen Innes, New South Wales for July 2021
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Sunday 17 October 2021   IDCJDW2047.202107
Most observations from Glen Innes, but some from Glen Innes Airport.
Temperature, humidity, cloud, evaporation and rainfall observations are from Glen Innes Ag Research Stn {station 056013}
Wind and pressure observations are from Glen Innes Airport AWS {station 056243}
